{"tid":1583530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢安全］parachute X藍牙耳機保平安","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T16:22:37.000Z","uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9a621d9fff980abb65faa754691a7c235a01b1","tid":1583530,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"我相信大家都有down parachute，唔識就睇依條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/02/parachute%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591-%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%2594%25A8add-on%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%259B%25B4%25E8%25BF%2585%25E9%2580%259F/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2Fparachute%2525E7%252582%2525BA%2525E6%2525B8%2525AF%2525E4%2525BA%2525BA%2525E6%2525B1%252582%2525E6%252595%252591-%2525E9%252581%25258B%2525E7%252594%2525A8add-on%2525E6%2525B1%252582%2525E5%25258A%2525A9%2525E6%25259B%2525B4%2525E8%2525BF%252585%2525E9%252580%25259F%2Famp%2F&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG15bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=b6012685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/02/parachute%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591-%25E9%2581%258B%25E7%2594%25A8add-on%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%259B%25B4%25E8%25BF%2585%25E9%2580%259F/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\nIphone 的巴打有siri可以用語音啟動求救，通知朋友親戚，但是有一個缺點是放在褲袋收唔到你求救暗號，所以希望各位加購一個藍牙耳機保平安，咁樣就唔洗囉部電話出來都可以收到各位求救暗號。<br />\n<br />\n如果有更好意見，歡迎各位提出，安全要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e01d2f3e0af53f9ddb87001ad3d35818188dc1","tid":1583530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"0996c4dc880ed51da89d061b3cc6eae3ac37eb08","tid":1583530,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc1e08af16d85c2b7793c1a02b1fa0ba7f61fe4","tid":1583530,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407e9ec49b4e45e23ca5995f5d7725206ed551f2","tid":1583530,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47eb2ba9997fe34dec0413952e592b8c2e2b6dfb","tid":1